{"tid":2241014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃之鋒：港大要人！踢走共青團大陸校委］網上投票！重奪研委會（附教學）","createTime":"2020-10-13T05:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:55:22.000Z","uid":79159,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7f25473f796310037d0acace60bbd81f0b3589","tid":2241014,"uid":79159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知港大個Master研委會俾支那仔佔據多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過去曾推動<span class=\"red\">刪除繁體中文為官方語言</span>、<span class=\"red\">貼公告譴責</span>反送中示威者，還<span class=\"red\">投票贊成解僱戴耀廷</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家有龐大WeChat網絡，輕鬆叫到幾百人投票穩贏<br />\n今年難得少左支那人入學，香港人要爭返口氣<br />\n自己地方的大學，點可以俾人佔據？<br />\n<br />\n時：10月12日-10月14日，10點至5點<br />\n地：網上投票呀！<a href=\"https://sweb.hku.hk/webservice3/servlet/Voting/menu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsweb.hku.hk%2Fwebservice3%2Fservlet%2FVoting%2Fmenu&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=e6c40f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://sweb.hku.hk/webservice3/servlet/Voting/menu</a><br />\n人：所有master生，<strong><span class=\"large\">parttime都可以投</span></strong>！！<br />\n投邊個：屌你老味見到Zhang，Wang呢啲，自己識揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">一蚊都唔使俾，唔使入研委會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入Link即投票 ，10秒投完快撚過你簽聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票連結：<a href=\"https://sweb.hku.hk/webservice3/servlet/Voting/menu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsweb.hku.hk%2Fwebservice3%2Fservlet%2FVoting%2Fmenu&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=e6c40f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sweb.hku.hk/webservice3/servlet/Voting/menu</a><br />\n<br />\n// 「內地候選人有共青團背景，有中聯辦拉票，佢哋完全唔宣傳都可以自動有幾百票，相反，香港學生多數係 Part-time Student，對港大無咩歸屬感，所以好難搵到佢哋投票」，問到認為內地生常勝有何關鍵？葉子健這樣解釋。<br />\n「事實係，我根本無辦法知道研究生民意係咩，因為大陸嘅學生根本無諮詢過其他人，咩資訊都剩係放晒上微信，連選舉宣傳都無，佢完全無理過香港學生的意見，因為佢無論點都已經『坐定粒六』啦。」葉子健說：「我唔想再望住內地學生鵲巢鳩占。」//<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%94%B1%E9%8B%AA%E8%B7%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%88%B0%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%81%9C%E7%95%99-%E8%91%89%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94-%E5%8F%AA%E6%83%B3%E5%A5%AA%E5%9B%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A9%B1%E8%AA%9E%E6%AC%8A/?fbclid=IwAR2BVk3U3JucXIaJbfUGihpnGWWXLYuXc58JBvzFXWziPi4WW_L4n_zspG0#.X4KZedARFqg.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%258B%25AA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2595%2599-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2BVk3U3JucXIaJbfUGihpnGWWXLYuXc58JBvzFXWziPi4WW_L4n_zspG0%23.X4KZedARFqg.facebook&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c7600ea7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%258B%25AA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2595%2599-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2BVk3U3JucX